  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA98">
<l>imañcūḻ malaiyu miruvicumpuṅ kāṟṟu</l>
<l>mamañcūḻn taṟaviḷaṅkit tōṉṟu – namaṉcūḻ</l>
<l>narakattu nammai naṇukāmaṟ kāppāṉ</l>
<l>ṟurakattai vāypiḷantāṉ ṟoṭṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the mountains embraced by snow, as the vast sky and as wind,</l>
<l>he appears fully luminous all around(?) ,</l>
<l>the one who protects us from getting near hell embraced by Yama,</l>
<l>the one who by touch tore open the mouth of the horse.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
